STATE of North Carolina
v.
Javonta Marquez ELLIS and Stephon Deandre Jennings No. 197P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 22, 2016 Ms. Katherine Jane Allen, Durham, Assistant Appellate Defender, For Jennings, Stephon Deandre. Mr. Craig M. Cooley, Attorney at Law, For Ellis, Javonta Marquez. Mr. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, Mr. Jess D. Mekeel, Assistant Attorney General, Mr. Peter A. Regulski, Assistant Attorney General, Mr. Matthew Delbridge, District Attorney, For State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 23rd of May 2016 by Defendant (Javonta Marquez Ellis) in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 22nd of September 2016."
